<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-05-21T16:00:00-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-05-21T16:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-21T16:00:00-04:00</updated><title>最好的门铃摄像头</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/sxSidjIZg78EqJRBlKmHTpPiwcA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70564714 /VRG_ILLO_5012_K_Radtke_Doorbell_Buying_Guide.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Kristen Radtke / The Verge、Shutterstock 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;我们挑选最好的视频门铃摄像头来监视人员、包裹和任何东西其他的东西会穿过你的前廊。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22954554/best-video-doorbell-camera&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/22954554/best-video-doorbell-camera" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/22954554/best-video-doorbell-camera</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-21T15:31:12-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-21T15:31:12-04:00</updated><title> August智能锁终于有了指纹选项</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;房子外面的黑色无线键盘。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/LZv3ldSsmngQ1cH8lj478LGmbow=/0x0:8192x5461/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73361715/Yale_Keypad_Touch.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;无线 Yale Keypad Touch 为新型 Yale Approach 锁和多款 August 智能锁提供指纹和钥匙代码访问。&lt;/em>; |图片：耶鲁&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;PH6L1n&quot;>;八月非常适合&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23393163/best-smart-door-lock&quot;>;智能锁&lt;/a>;，但细心的观察者可能已经注意到，该公司尚未发布任何&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/1/8/21050994/august-wi-fi-smart- lock-yves-behar-deadbolt-price-design-features-ces&quot;>;四年内的新硬件&lt;/a>;。 August 锁的所有者可能会放心，因为&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Faugust.com%2Fproducts%2Fyale- keypad&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F5%2F21%2F24161777%2Faugust-smart-lock-yale-keypad-touch-fingerprint-unlock&quot; rel=&quot;赞助nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;新的无线键盘&lt;/a>;最终为他们带来了指纹解锁的选项。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;xgSaUD&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://shopyalehome.com /pages/yale-keypad&quot;>;Yale Keypad Touch&lt;/a>; 是一款支持指纹的无线键盘，适用于 Yale 和 August 改装锁，可与第四代 August Wi-Fi 智能锁、第三代 August Smart Lock Pro 配合使用，第三代 August 智能锁，以及新的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/11/24126764/yale-approach-smart-lock-price-release-date-specs&quot;>;带 Wi-Fi 的耶鲁方法锁&lt;/a>;。除了指纹和代码解锁外，它还提供一键式锁定功能。现已在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://shopyalehome.com/&quot;>;ShopYaleHome.com&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs= 上发售，售价 109.99 美元1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Faugust.com%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F5%2F21%2F24161777%2Faugust-智能锁- yale-keypad-touch-fingerprint-unlock&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;August.com&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;SqxZdz&quot;>;对于那些已经有八月了...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/21/24161777/august-smart-lock-yale-keypad-touch-fingerprint -unlock&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/21/24161777/august-smart-lock-yale-keypad-touch-fingerprint-unlock" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/21/24161777/august-smart-lock-yale-keypad-touch-fingerprint-unlock</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-21T15:18:22-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-21T15:18:22-04:00</updated><title>有一个电盐勺可以增加鲜味</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;电盐勺放在桌子上，旁边有两个碗。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/WahLF3kmKPF81SbbfegTsM0b7Kk=/0x69:1088x794/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73361663/Top_About.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;一个厚实的电勺，用于盛放厚实的低钠食物。&lt;/em>; |图片：Kirin&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;tHmCNl&quot;>;如果您出于医疗原因或只是为了保持健康而从饮食中减少盐分，那么低钠食物可能会令人失望。但不要绝望——日本公司 Kirin 声称其&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kirinholdings.com/en/newsroom/release/2024/0520_01.html&quot;>;电盐勺&lt;/a提供了解决方案>;，它使用电极让你的舌头通电，给你带来一点咸味电击。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Ftd0NI&quot;>;这个想法，如&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reuters.com/technology/kirins-electric-spoon-leaps-ig-noble-infamy-dinner-table -2024-05-20/&quot;>;&lt;em>;路透社&lt;/em>;所说的&lt;/a>;是，它通过一个小电流来“将钠离子分子集中在舌头上”，从而增强咸味。这就像技术鲜味。该公司表示，其目标是让人们吃低钠食物，让他们吃得更健康，而不用因为食物的不咸而感到难过。 &lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Kirin&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;FYQFfg&quot;>;Kirin 与日本明治大学医学院的 Homei Miyashita 教授合作。 .&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/21/24161762/electric-salt-spoon-umami-flavor&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/21/24161762/electric-salt-spoon-umami-flavor" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/21/24161762/electric-salt-spoon-umami-flavor</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-21T15:15:01-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-21T15:15:01-04:00</updated><title> Square Enix 将让《王国之心》在 Steam 上烹饪</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;《王国之心》中唐纳德、索拉和高飞在仙境中的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/baaFPmHeOdBnw9r7JlecJ5Pe8Sg=/156x0:1509x902/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73361654/Screenshot_2024_05_21_at_2.38.4 6_PM.0.png &quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Square Enix&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;pvNZJY&quot;>;我最近一直有这些奇怪的想法...比如，我应该回去重播&lt;em>;是否是王国之心系列？幸运的是